      "date": "2017-08-30 04:17:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-43vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server 7.4/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/33cf2c80-2058-4d12-953b-c42c62fcc72a). Ran 16 tests. No failures.",
